a&amp;author=L+Minordi&amp;author=A+Vecchioli&amp;author=P+Marano&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;journal=Abdom+Imaging&amp;pages=326-334&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00261-003-0116-9&amp;pmid=15354341">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="b7-0291847" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Gourtsoyiannis N, Papanikolaou N, Grammatikakis J, Papamastorakis G, Prassopoulos P, Roussomoustakaki M. Assessment of Crohn’s disease activity in the small bowel with MR and conventional enteroclysis: preliminary results. <em>Eur Radiol</em> 2004;14(6): 1017–1024.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00330-004-2302-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15057562/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Assessment+of+Crohn%E2%80%99s+disease+activity+in+the+small+bowel+with+MR+and+conventional+enteroclysis%3A+preliminary+results&amp;author=N+Gourtsoyiannis&amp;author=N+Papanikolaou&amp;author=J+Grammatikakis&amp;author=G+Papamastorakis&amp;author=P+Prassopoulos&amp;author=M+Roussomoustakaki&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;journal=Eur+Radiol&amp;pages=1017-1024&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00330-004-2302-8&amp;pmid=15057562">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="b8-0291847" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Chou CK, Chen LT, Sheu RS, Wang ML, Jaw TS, Liu GC. MRI manifestations of gastrointestinal wall thickening. <em>Abdom Imaging</em> 1994;19(5):389–394.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/BF00206921">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7950809/">PubMed</a></div><div class